        "id": "clkrnuwrx001ul40gjtobq4bp",
        "title": "How do I enrol if I do not have smartphone? \r\nCan my caregiver enrol me on his/her HealthHub app? ",
        "body": null,
        "createdAt": "2023-08-01T02:09:12.795Z",
        "published": true,
        "publishedAt": "2023-08-01T05:56:36.171Z",
        "priority": 0,
        "answer": {
            "id": "clkrnuwrx001vl40gn2eaysfe",
            "body": "<p>You can grant access to your family members or loved ones to assist you with the enrolment by adding them as your caregiver in HealthHub and enabling permission to manage Healthier SG on your behalf. You may access the HealthHub app by using your caregiver's smartphone. Your caregiver can then add you as a care recipient to view your health records and manage your e-Services on HealthHub.</p><p><br></p><p>You will need your Singpass account to authorise your caregiver via HealthHub. If you do not have a Singpass account, you may register for Singpass through <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.singpass.gov.sg/home/ui/register/instructions\">this website</a> or head down to the nearest Singpass counter for assistance, with your caregiver and bring along both your NRICs. For Singpass counter locations, click <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.singpass.gov.sg/home/ui/counter-locations\">here</a>.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Follow the steps below to first add a caregiver.</strong></p><p><img crossorigin=\"anonymous\" src=\"https://d33wubrfki0l68.cloudfront.net/fe760e859f659582ddad459db6aeb5f08347baf4/9b940/images/guide/slide1.png\" alt=\"faq\"><img crossorigin=\"anonymous\" src=\"https://d33wubrfki0l68.cloudfront.net/42fadaa16f7fb2f2c947c7dd7a355b15a5dd0e28/ad3b3/images/guide/slide2.png\" alt=\"faq\"></p><p><strong>Please ensure that you have enabled \"Healthier SG\" access in the Caregiver's Details page (as shown in Step 5).</strong></p><p><br></p><p>After this has been done, inform your caregiver to add your Health Profile under <strong>Add Loved ones</strong>, using his/her own HealthHub account.</p><p><img crossorigin=\"anonymous\" src=\"https://d33wubrfki0l68.cloudfront.net/9e0359e6ff8318aa49366c09a27a3e2bf9e7f560/d322d/images/guide/slide3.png\" alt=\"faq\"><img crossorigin=\"anonymous\" src=\"https://d33wubrfki0l68.cloudfront.net/f228cc6812c248cb4cb4d7e32ed4b2829572d7a9/a9920/images/guide/slide4.png\" alt=\"faq\"></p><p>Once your caregiver has successfully added you as a care recipient, your user profile will be shown on HealthHub for them to assist with your enrolment if you are eligible to enrol in Healthier SG.</p><p>Alternatively, you may enrol in Healthier SG through the <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.healthhub.sg/\">HealthHub web portal</a> on a computer device and logging in with your Singpass.</p><p><br></p><p>HealthHub FAQs can be found <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.healthhub.sg/faqs\">here</a>.</p>",
            "updatedAt": "2023-08-01T05:56:36.059Z",
            "numPositiveFeedback": 5
        },
