            "id": "clvqgz7pv002rjnkb00nh0q2l",
            "body": "<p>Your first onboarding Health Plan consultation with your first Healthier SG clinic is fully-subsidised. Subsequent Health Plan check-ins are fully-subsidised as well.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>If you are visiting for other non-Healthier SG consultations (e.g. for illnesses such as colds or coughs) at the same time as Health Plan first visit, those non-Healthier SG related consultations will be chargeable.</p>",
