            "body": "<p>Yes, patients have a choice of which subsidy tier (Healthier SG Chronic Tier or existing CHAS Chronic Tier) they would like to claim from for each visit.</p><br><p>Healthier SG benefits and subsidies are available/accessible at your enrolled Healthier SG clinic.</p>",
