        "title": "Can I claim for subsidies for different chronic condition(s) under the new Healthier SG Chronic Tier and existing CHAS Chronic Tier respectively during the same visit? \n(E.g. Chronic condition 1 may be more beneficial under the new Healthier SG Chronic Tier because it requires selected chronic medications, whereas chronic condition 2 may be better off under the existing CHAS Chronic Tier)",
